<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<title>Confirmation of Your Request | AuthenticPage</title>
		<style>
			@media screen and(max-width: 600px) {
				.container {
					width: 100% !important;
				}
				.button {
					width: 100% !important;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #F3F4F6; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #374151;">
		<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
			<tr>
				<td style="padding: 20px 0;">
					<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="600" style="margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;" class="container">
						<tr>
							<td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F46E5, #6366F1); padding: 32px 20px; text-align: center;">
								<img src="https://authenticpage.com/logo_528.png" alt="AuthenticPage Logo" style="width: 120px; height: auto; margin-bottom: 16px;">
								<h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0;">Confirmation of Your Request</h1>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td style="padding: 32px 24px;">
								<p style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 16px;">Hello
									{{ demande.demandeur.name }},</p>
								<p>We confirm that your request has been received and recorded in our system.</p>
								<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 24px 0; background-color: #F3F4F6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px;">
									<tr>
										<td>
											<h2 style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 18px;">Details of Your Request:</h2>
											<p>
												<strong>Title:</strong>
												{{ demande.intitule }}</p>
											<p>
												<strong>Date of Request:</strong>
												{{ dateDemande }}</p>
											<p>
												<strong>Year of Acquisition:</strong>
												{{ anneeObtention }}</p>

											<p>
												<strong>Requesting Institution:</strong>
												{{ institutDemandeur.name }}</p>

										</td>
									</tr>
								</table>
								<p>We will process your request as soon as possible. You will receive a notification as soon as updates are available.</p>
								<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
									<tr>
										<td>
											<a href="https://authenticpage.com/auth/sign-in" style="background-color: #4F46E5; color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block;" class="button">Track My Request</a>
										</td>
									</tr>
								</table>
								<p>If you have any questions or need additional information, please do not hesitate to contact us.</p>
							</td>
						</tr>
						{% include './footer.html.twig' %}

					</table>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
	</body>
</html>
